<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">ילד</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
ילד / yâlad / yaw-lad'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''ילד'''

# To bear young; causatively to [[beget]]; medically to act as midwife; specifically to show lineage: - bear, beget, birth ([-day]), born, (make to) bring forth (children, young), bring up, calve, child, come, be delivered (of a child), time of delivery, gender, hatch, labour, (do the office of a) midwife, declare pedigrees, be the son of, (woman in, woman that) travail (-eth, -ing woman).

